title: The Smoothie Recipe Book: 150 Smoothie Recipes
description:
The Smoothie Recipe Book: 150 Smoothie Recipes Including Smoothies for Weight Loss and Smoothies for Optimum Health by Rockridge Press
English | 2013 | ISBN: 1623151015 | ISBN-13: 9781623151010 | 128 pages | EPUB | 0,8 MB

Who doesn't love smoothies? The Smoothie Recipe Book is the ultimate resource for creating delicious and nutritious smoothies.
Packed with superfoods and antioxidants, 150 delicious smoothie recipes provide vitamins and minerals the way nature intended.

The Smoothie Recipe Book offers nutrient-rich smoothies to cleanse, lose weight, improve health, and increase energy.
